column8: The maiden and I, we're proud to be of service, Your Highness.
Something I can do for you?
We shall help get you on your way.
Can I interest you in one of these?
I hope I may be of service.
What can I do for you?
I hope you find this aid useful.
I was merely resting these old bones.
You cannot kill what is already dead.
You may try all you like.
Let your feelings out, if you wish.
Prince, I could use your aid...
This is my punishment alone, but... there's a spare shovel...
You do brighten up this place. A little.
I am glad you showed up.
I believe you are strong enough to do as you wish, Prince.
We hope you are successful, Prince

That is quite an undertaking, Prince. If it wasn't you yourself proposing it, I'd like to call it madness, truth be told. However, I have seen what you are capable of. Here, I've got something could be of some help.
Your Majesty, if you're to be so generous with me, I intend to repay the favour. So, take this, with my compliments.
Hm, thank you. This will brace me for the next century of digging, at least. Here, take this, with my gratitude.
Caught me on a break again. Ha.
How nice to see you, Prince.
I can be of help, Prince.
Think I can do that, Prince.
Got that right here, your Highness.
You have a definite strength, Highness.
Do tell the Chosen I said hello.
May you get out of here this time, Highness.
Think he'll go all the way this time, maiden?
That's one fight you shall not win.
Takes more than that to disperse the maiden, Prince.
If you have so much energy, you can help me dig.
The maiden is stronger than you or I.
There's no need for that here, Prince.
Make no attempt to hurt her, Prince.
She could siphon all of your life force in a blink, if she so wished.
You're more likely to hurt yourself.
The maiden has no part in this.
We shall come to your aid, Highness.
The maiden wishes to join the fray...
Let's get the drop on her.
How do you fare, Master Aphelios?
Why if it isn't Master Aphelios.
We are here for you, Highness.
We are here support you, Prince.
The maiden will unleash her power.
What good would that do here?
Call us when you need us.
The maiden appreciates the chance to get out.
Thanks on behalf of the maiden, there.
The maiden is... rather happy right now.
I cannot remember life before her, Prince.
You have earned the maiden's favor, Prince.
Your offering has been accepted, Prince.
I think the maiden is warming up to you.
The maiden is a very good listener.
You have been blessed by the maiden.
I do prefer the peace and quiet...
Thank you for picking up a bit.
Break all the pots you like.
Oh those shades aren't so bad.
No need for that here, Prince.
They'll just come back next time.
Those shades are stuck here, Prince.
Oh, I'll just stash that one away, then, Prince.
Is that for me, Prince? Well then, all right.
I'll take that off your hands if you insist, Highness.
I've not much need of that, but I can take it, Prince.
Come now, Highness, you really shouldn't have.
Please don't take this the wrong way, Prince, but I cannot accept something like this.
Apologies, Prince. But I've no need of that. You'd best hang onto it.
Afraid I have no need for that, Highness, though I appreciate the gesture there.
Thank you, Prince, though I've no use for this right now.
Your Highness, I was wondering if you might hear me out.
Prince, I've a small favor I would ask of you if you don't mind.
Wanted to ask you something here, Highness.
Quick request if you've a moment for us, Prince.
Oh, this is rather good, your highness.
Is that for me really, Highness? That stuff brings back fond memories...
Look at what the Prince has brought for us, maiden.
On behalf of the maiden and myself, we're very grateful for your gesture here.
Oh, look how happy she is.
